                                                2.4 Walk-In Orders
                                            </strong>
                                            <p>Employees are authorized to create orders on behalf of walk-in customers and add them to the system for tracking and fulfillment.</p>
                                            <h5>
                                                3. Customer Support
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>Customers may reach out for support or inquiries through available communication channels.</p>
                                            <p>Employees and the owner are available to address order-related concerns, including updates on order statuses or other queries.</p>
