                                                5. Disclaimers
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>Infinity Prints is not responsible for delays caused by unforeseen circumstances such as natural disasters, technical issues, or supply chain disruptions.</p>
                                            <p>Customers are responsible for providing accurate order information. Errors resulting from customer-provided details are not the responsibility of the business.</p>
