                                                6. Changes to Terms and Conditions
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>These terms and conditions are subject to change without prior notice.</p>
                                            <p>Updated terms will be communicated via our website or in-store.</p>

                                            <h4>
                                                Account Security
                                            </h4>
                                            <h5>
                                                1. Account Creation and Responsibility
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>  Customers are responsible for creating and maintaining a secure password for their accounts. </p>
                                            <p> Infinity Prints recommends using a strong password that includes a combination of uppercase and lowercase letters, numbers, and symbols.</p>
                                            <p> Customers are solely responsible for all activity that occurs under their account. </p>
