                                                1.2 Confidentiality
                                            </h5>
                                            <p> Customers must keep their account information, including passwords and any other sensitive data, confidential and not share it with unauthorized individuals.</p>
                                            <p> Customers must notify Infinity Prints immediately of any suspected unauthorized use of their account or any security breach.</p>
                                            <h5>
                                                1.3 Account Access
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>Infinity Prints reserves the right to suspend or terminate a customer's account if it suspects any fraudulent activity or violation of these Terms and Conditions.</p>
                                            <h5>
                                                1.4 Data Security
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>Infinity Prints takes reasonable measures to protect customer data from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.</p>
                                            <p> However, Infinity Prints cannot guarantee the complete security of any data transmitted over the internet or stored electronically. This is due to potential risks posed by hackers and other cyber threats that exist in the digital space. While our website has security measures to protect your information, it is important to acknowledge that no system can be entirely immune to such risks.</p>


                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>




